text:
The Biryani is great and delicious! I had it with their curry chicken.
The Biryani rice is not wet and not oily; it was very fluffy and it complements the rich, chicken curry sauce.
The stall's service was great, and they were very patient with my questions.

Ordered curry chicken bryani coz owner said cannot make fried chicken hot.
Rice cold, curry bitter, curry chicken cold.
Disappointing from a stall with bryani in the name
Our fav briyani shop at Taman Jurong. Very yums! Always adding extra rice and extra sides to share.
The Yaseen Singapore Biryani of Nagoor traditional trend, India make Nagoor Biryani to feed children at The Hallal Mutton and Children's Home in Nagoor Master

Very good and tasty.  Price worthy.
